  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Oh... You're the one who returned the book to my dad! Did you give it back to my dad? Ah... My dad... he doesn't worry about me... The only thing he cares about is that stupid book... Aren't I right?"
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "You look much stronger than last time... Can you do me a favor? I got a request from the fairies in #m10002000#... There are many baby fairies and we should make houses for them... What do you think? Can you collect the materials to build those houses?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Wow~ Thanks! Then first, can you collect #b30 #t4000019#s and 30 #t4000027#s#k by taking down #r#o19#s and #o31#s#k? They come from such weak monsters… so it might be a bit boring… hehe… This is only the beginning, though. I’m counting on you!"
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Yeah... You can't take a request from a kid... yeah... right... If you change your mind, please let me know... I can't do this on my own..."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Wow... You collected them all! Cool~ Isn't it fun to hunt weak monsters? No? Oh come on~ Anyway I will give these to the fairies... But I don't think this is enough."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "I got the materials... Yeah... It was a good idea to ask you for a favor... Thanks... but there are still more things to get. Whenever you're ready, please talk to me again!"
        }
      },
